profile: Conway is a family-owned, 30,000sqft Furniture and Flooring destination in Listowel Ontario - with a La-Z-Boy custom studio, Palliser gallery, full mattress gallery, and full flooring department specializing in custom flooring, hardwood and tile installs of all sizes. Conway is known for their upfront pricing (tax & delivery always included!), knowledgeable and friendly staff, and 'over-and-above' service in the industry that ensures you are taken care of for the life of your furniture or flooring.
